<P>
Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ACCIDENT VICTIMS; SETTLEMENTS; DAMAGES; TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS -- TEXAS; TOYOTA 
MOTOR CORP 
</P>
