</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Pinnacle West Capital Corp. announced that its board decided at a special 
meeting to reject an acquisition proposal by PacifiCorp, which it called 
inadequate . . . Benton Harbor, Mich.-based Whirlpool Corp. said it has agreed 
to acquire 28.4% of Toronto-based Inglis Ltd. that it does not already own for 
about $40. 
</P>
