<P>
BANKRUPTCY; CORPORATE RESTRUCTURING; LOAN DEFAULTS; BELL SAVINGS &amp; LOAN 
ASSOCIATION; BOONE, PAT; LAMB &amp; LION RECORDS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
