<P>
TRW INC; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; LASERS; LASER WEAPONS; 
SCIENTISTS; ARMS CONTROL; WEAPONS INSPECTION; STRATEGIC DEFENSE INITIATIVE 
</P>
