Back in Black, AC/DC (Atlantic) 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
VIDEO RENTALS 
</P>
<P>
A look at the fast-moving video rentals in three Orange County neighborhoods. 
</P>
<P>
VIDEO CITY, 1823 W. Orangethorpe Ave., Fullerton. (714) 870-6130. 
</P>
<P>
Ghostbusters II (RCA) 
</P>
<P>
Scrooged (Paramount) 
</P>
<P>
Three Fugitives (Touchstone) 
</P>
<P>
Leviathan (MGM-UA) 
</P>
<P>
Batman (Warner Bros.) 
</P>
<P>
