ANGELES COUNTY -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES; POLICE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; PRISONS 
-- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; TERRORISM -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; CROSS BURNING; RACIAL 
