<P>
JEWS -- USSR; JEWS -- LOS ANGELES; USSR -- EMIGRATION; UNITED STATES -- 
IMMIGRATION; UNITED STATES -- POPULATION; LOS ANGELES -- POPULATION; REFUGEES 
-- USSR 
